            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1695044250403-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1695044250403-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>curry powder</strong> with a drizzle of the <strong>coconut stock</strong> (save the rest for later!) in a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken strips</strong>, then mix well and set aside to marinate</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-low heat</p>",
