    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Thai-style chicken</strong> over the<strong> satay salad with pickled cucumber </strong>– this is your <strong>lighter chicken satay salad with pickled cucumber</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>remaining satay sauce</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
